CREATE TABLE [dbo].[LOG]
(
 cycle INT ,
 [schema] VARCHAR ,
 [table] VARCHAR ,
 [row_count] VARCHAR ,
 [distinct_row_count] VARCHAR ,
 [column] VARCHAR ,
 [status] VARCHAR ,
 [start_time] DATETIME2 ,
 [end_time] DATETIME2 ,
 [duration(s)] VARCHAR ,
 [duration(min)] VARCHAR ,
 [error] VARCHAR ,
 [line_number] INT ,
 [LOG_O_YEAR] INT ,
 [LOG_O_MONTH] INT ,
 [LOG_O_DAY] INT ,
 [LOG_O_HOUR] INT ,
 [LOG_O_MIN] INT ,
 [LOG_APPLICATION_NAME] VARCHAR 
)
